node.text:
Did YOU know Scotland has some of the best dark skies in Europe?! ✨💫 Due to large areas of low light pollution, on a clear night, constellations of stars, the planets, the Milky Way galaxy & even the Northern Lights can be spotted! ⭐🌟 Brilliant shot by @martindonaldsmith taken at Smailholm Tower in the Scottish Borders 📷

#SmailholmTower #Kelso #ScottishBorders #SeeSouthScotland #Scotland #VisitScotland #ScotlandStartsHere
